Overview






BHR Capital LLC seeks to provide, through a value-oriented investment strategy, high absolute and risk-adjusted returns with relatively low correlations to broad U.S. equity and credit market indices. We focus on event-driven investment opportunities, including special situations, possessing one or more catalysts to unlock value. We believe rigorous fundamental research, coupled with various hedging strategies, provides the most effective protection from capital losses. The principals of BHR Capital LLC have substantial capital invested alongside our partners, as we believe this is the single best way to ensure an alignment of interests.
 









