Company Overview of BHR Capital LLC



Snapshot People




Company Overview
BHR Capital LLC is an employee owned hedge fund sponsor. The firm primarily provides its services to pooled investment vehicles. It manages client focused equity and fixed income portfolios. The firm invests in public equity, fixed income, and hedging markets of the United States. It typically invests in value stocks of companies. The firm also employs event driven investing. It employs fundamental research to make its investments. The firm uses internal research to create its portfolios. BHR Capital LLC was founded in October, 2009 and is based in New York City.


