Michael Neal Thompson CFA: Executive Profile & Biography - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 26, 2017 11:10 AM ET
Capital Markets

Company Overview of BHR Capital LLC



SnapshotPeople 




OverviewBoard MembersCommittees



Executive Profile
Michael Neal Thompson CFAManaging Partner and Portfolio Manager, BHR Capital LLCAgeTotal Calculated CompensationThis person is connected to 0 Board Members in 0 different organizations across 0 different industries.----
Background

		Mr. Michael Neal Thompson serves as the Managing Partner and Portfolio Manager at BHR Capital LLC. Mr. Thompson is responsible for all portfolio construction, security selection, and risk management activities and oversees the firm’s investment team. He co-founded the firm in 2009. Prior to this, Mr. Thompson was the Managing Director and Principal at Bay Harbour Management L.C. Mr. Thompson became a Portfolio Manager at the firm in January 2009. He had joined the firm ... in 2008 to lead research and investment efforts in the financial and real estate sectors, and to manage the firm’s short investment portfolio. Before that, Mr. Thompson was the Managing Director and Deputy Global Head of Structured Credit Products at Wachovia Securities. He also had direct responsibility for a proprietary trading book which exceeded $3 billion in notional value. In addition, Mr. Thompson managed the Financial Institutions Capital Solutions Group at the firm which focused on insurance-linked products. He was responsible for the firm’s structured arbitrage business. Prior to that, Mr. Thompson was in charge of the firm’s emerging products business and led the team which created a stand-alone provider of repo and total return swaps. He has an extensive experiece in investing and trading, structuring, and risk management of transactions across corporate debt and equity, structured finance, real estate securities, and other asset classes. Mr. Thompson is a Chartered Financial Analyst designation holder. He holds a B.B.A. degree, Magna Cum Laude in International Finance from the Honors Program at University of Georgia, where Mr. Thompson received Alumni, Governor’s, and Hope Scholarships.Read Full Background




